          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV",
                "EDEG",
                "GSPEC",
                "SITA"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Five irradiations were",
                "carried out between ?-energies of 4.0 and 6.3 MeV. The",
                "beam intensity was between 100 and 250 nA. The length",
                "of irradiations varied between 14 and 25 hours.",
                "Irradiations were done in Faraday-cup type target",
                "chamber. The current integrator counts were recorded",
                "in multichannel scaling mode with 1 min time base.",
                "Suppressor voltage of -300V was applied.",
                "The temperature and pressure of the target gas was",
                "monitored. The target window was 1 micron pinhole-free",
                "Ni foil. Be7 products were collected on a copper",
                "catcher disk which was measured after irradiation on",
                "a HPGe detector using 1 cm distance."
              ]
            }
          ],
